==English==

===Noun===
'''imprudence'''

# The quality or state of being [[imprudent]]; want of [[prudence]], [[caution]], [[discretion]] or [[circumspection]]; [[indiscretion]]; [[inconsideration]]; [[rashness]]; [[heedlessness]].
